# Exclude heavy directories from Docker build context
# (workspace root is used as context for pnpm monorepo builds)

.git
.github
.claude
.npmrc
node_modules
**/node_modules
**/.next
**/dist
**/build
**/coverage
**/.turbo
**/tsconfig.tsbuildinfo

# Docs and non-source files
docs
notes
*.md
*.sarif
gitleaks-results.sarif/
